{"id":65,"parent_id":64,"book_id":9,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":65,"title":"JST, Romans 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"JST, Rom.","uri":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rom/3","content":[[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"t1","uri":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rom/3.t1","order":"12.14.003.448"},[".title",["b","JST, Romans 3:5–8."],"Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/3.5-8"},"Romans 3:5–8"]],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rom/3.5","order":".003.449"},["b","5"],"But if",["i","we remain in"],"our unrighteousness",["i","and"],"commend the righteousness of God,",["i","how dare"],"we say, God is unrighteous who taketh vengeance? (I speak as a man",["i","who fears God,"],")"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rom/3.6","order":".003.450"},["b","6"],"God forbid; for then how shall God judge the world?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rom/3.7","order":".003.451"},["b","7"],"For if the truth of God hath more abounded through my lie,",["i","(as it is called of the Jews,)"],"unto his glory; why yet am I also judged as a sinner? and not",["i","received? Because"],"we",["i","are"],"slanderously reported;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rom/3.8","order":".003.452"},["b","8"],"And some affirm that we say,",["i","(whose damnation is just,)"],"Let us do evil that good may come.",["i","But this is false."]]]]],"refs":null}
